TextChange: While materialsm is not necessarily a 'new thing,' it most certainly takes center stage in the complaint contest of the new age.
Be it the younger generations' tendencies or technological innovation and advancement taking away traditional hardships,
This 'new' quirk of the modern era is actually not that new at all and for it to be used against the wave of modern society is rather hypocritical.
